abstract: >
  SFA-Bench is a model-agnostic benchmark for sealed, replayable AI reasoning
  failures and tamper-evident failure history. It preserves failure artifacts,
  verifies replayability, tracks recurrence, and supports offline transcript
  normalization, re-derivation, and an optional live adapter boundary without
  live model calls in CI.
